ERIEC.LayerComposition.viableToHilbert_maps_bool_isos_equal :
  viableToHilbertFunctor.map boolIdentityIso = viableToHilbertFunctor.map boolToggleIso
ERIEC.LayerComposition.viableToHilbert_not_faithful : ¬Function.Injective fun f => viableToHilbertFunctor.map f
ERIEC.LayerComposition.no_bool_hom_left_inverse :
  ¬∃ recover, ∀ (f : boolViableObject ⟶ boolViableObject), recover (viableToHilbertFunctor.map f) = f
'ERIEC.LayerComposition.viableToHilbert_not_faithful' depends on axioms: [propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]
'ERIEC.LayerComposition.no_bool_hom_left_inverse' depends on axioms: [propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]
